{"tid":2253980,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「沙德爾」逼港1號風球生效　天文台午夜後改發3號波","createTime":"2020-10-22T13:38:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-02T23:41:51.000Z","uid":25823,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"bfa316fa172d2cc02860e998223d4434761fc3a7","tid":2253980,"uid":25823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T13:38:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QwPkE8W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQwPkE8W.jpg&h=d52afb6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n強烈熱帶風暴「沙德爾」已增強為颱風，並逐漸靠近廣東沿岸地區，並轉向偏西方向移動。天文台於今日(22日)下午5時40分發出一號戒備信號，按照預測路徑，「沙德爾」會繼續移近華南沿岸，與其相關的強風會逐漸影響珠江口一帶。天文台會在午夜後改發3號強風信號。<br />\n天文台預測現時影響廣東沿岸的東北季候風會在明早逐漸增強，未來數天沿岸地區及南海北部風勢頗大。預料高空反氣旋將會在下周初增強，華南天色好轉。此外，一個廣闊低壓區會在下周中期影響南海中部。"},{"pid":"0d2bb661e313f54eaaf9147381c3beb6ee947284","tid":2253980,"uid":125357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T13:39:54.000Z","msg":"好大乳"},{"pid":"bf68fbc30bf6a33311ac5e4a0dc63ffd77298e4a","tid":2253980,"uid":165022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T13:41:03.000Z","msg":"個風球咁大點得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d601a37936024db894c52a15f09837b4d6075e04","tid":2253980,"uid":25823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T13:42:11.000Z","msg":"大乳師"},{"pid":"633625f9b2c6fbabe76073c765da555107e00591","tid":2253980,"uid":45910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf68fbc30bf6a33311ac5e4a0dc63ffd77298e4a","tid":2253980,"uid":165022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T13:41:03.000Z","msg":"個風球咁大點得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T13:47:21.000Z","msg":"八字波<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f0577d79c0ef828f312a6f6a7878408f1df3cd7","tid":2253980,"uid":260694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T13:51:38.000Z","msg":"好大"},{"p